name: Datahole
description:
Fill the holes in the data with the right file as fast as you can, before you are overrun with viruses that threaten your computer.

Use the temporary storage of the cache wisely to assist when times get tense, and take advantage of the occasional 'wildfile' that can fit anywhere.

How long can you survive?
